Package: postshock
Type: Package
Title: Implement Post-Shock Forecasting Methodology With an Intercept Correction Modeling Framework
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("David", "Lundquist", email = "davidpatricklundquist@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Daniel J.", "Eck", email = "dje13@illinois.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: David Lundquist <davidpatricklundquist@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions for forecasting in a post-shock time series setting using an intercept correction framework. The framework assumes a post-shock intercept correction term, estimated by aggregating outside information.
